# Competitor Spy Module — Trung tâm Minh bạch Quảng cáo

Tạo module mới **"Theo dõi đối thủ"** (Competitor Spy) sử dụng dữ liệu từ Google Ads Transparency Center (Trung tâm minh bạch quảng cáo) để giúp user:

1. **Tìm kiếm theo domain** — xem tất cả quảng cáo đang chạy trên domain đó
2. **Tìm kiếm theo media buyer** — xem media buyer nào đang chạy ads trên domain nào
3. **Tạo spy target** — theo dõi domain/media buyer và nhận alert khi có thay đổi
4. **Tích hợp Project Management** — nút "Spy đối thủ" trên mỗi dự án

---

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Data Model & Types

#### [NEW] [competitor-spy-types.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosProjectProPrototype/src/types/competitor-spy-types.ts)

New type definitions for the spy module:

```typescript
// Core entities
SpyDomain          // Domain being tracked (domain, advertiser info, ad count, last checked)
SpyMediaBuyer      // Media buyer profile (name, email, verified, domains they run ads on)
SpyAd              // Individual ad creative (format, content, assets, first/last seen, platform, region)
SpyTarget          // User-created spy target (type: domain|media_buyer, alert settings, status)
SpyAlert           // Change notification (type: new_ad|removed_ad|new_buyer|creative_change, timestamp)
SpySearchResult    // Search result wrapper
```

Key type relationships:
- `SpyDomain` → has many `SpyAd[]` and many `SpyMediaBuyer[]`
- `SpyMediaBuyer` → runs ads on many `SpyDomain[]`
- `SpyTarget` → references either a `SpyDomain` or `SpyMediaBuyer`
- `SpyAlert` → references a `SpyTarget`

---

### 2. Mock Data

#### [NEW] [mock-competitor-spy-data.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosProjectProPrototype/src/data/mock-competitor-spy-data.ts)

Rich mock data simulating Google Ads Transparency Center results:
- **5+ sample domains** (binance.com, shopee.vn, lazada.vn, tiki.vn, sendo.vn) with realistic ad creatives
- **10+ media buyers** with Vietnamese names, emails, verified status
- **30+ sample ads** across formats: Text, Image, Video
- **Sample alerts** for change detection
- Realistic metadata: regions (VN, TH, ID), platforms (YouTube, Search, Display, Maps), date ranges

---

### 3. State Management

#### [NEW] [useCompetitorSpyStore.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosProjectProPrototype/src/hooks/useCompetitorSpyStore.tsx)

Context + Reducer store (same pattern as `useProjectCampaignStore`):
- **State**: domains, mediaBuyers, ads, targets, alerts, search results, loading states
- **Actions**: SEARCH_DOMAIN, SEARCH_MEDIA_BUYER, ADD_SPY_TARGET, REMOVE_SPY_TARGET, TOGGLE_TARGET_ALERT, MARK_ALERT_READ, SIMULATE_CRAWL

