## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `npm run dev` — verify no build errors
- Navigate to `/competitor-spy` — page loads without errors
- Search by domain/media buyer — results render correctly
- Add/remove spy targets — state updates correctly
- Alerts feed populates with mock data

### Manual Verification
- Sidebar shows new "Theo dõi đối thủ" nav item
- All UI components render correctly in both light/dark mode
- Collapsible left panel works
- Ad creative cards display different formats (Text/Image/Video)
- "Spy đối thủ" button appears in project list and detail views
- Responsive layout at various screen sizes
